ik (f) ** Straight Seniors winner: {{flagicon|NED}} Jesse Thehu ** Teams winners: {{NOR}} (m) / {{GER}} (f) * August 23 – 26: Dynamic European Championships (U23) in {{flagicon|NED}} [[Heeze-Leende]] ** 8 balls winner: {{flagicon|GER}} Joshua Filler ** 9 balls winner: {{flagicon|GER}} Joshua Filler * August 17 – 20: 9-Ball World Championship (Wheelchair) in {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Tampere]] ** Winners: {{flagicon|Illinois}} 5th Street Players, 2nd place: {{flagicon|California}} The Contenders II, 3rd place: {{flagicon|Illinois}} Here We Go Again & {{flagicon|Ontario}} 9-Ball Bombers * December 4 – 7: [[2017 Mosconi Cup]] in {{flagicon|USA}} Las Vegas ** Winner: {{flagicon|Europe}} Europe
