biu]] * September 24: #22 {{flagicon|LUX}} World Open [[Bertrange]] * September 23: #23 {{flagicon|POR}} World Open [[Lisbon]] * September 23 & 24: #24 {{flagicon|CRO}} World Open [[Zagreb]] * September 30 – October 1: #25 {{flagicon|SRB}} World Open [[Belgrade]] * September 30: #26 {{flagicon|CZE}} World Open [[Ostrava]] * October 7 & 8: #27 {{flagicon|RUS}} World Open [[Moscow]] * October 14 & 15: #28 {{flagicon|POL}} World Open [[Elbląg]] * October 21: #29 {{flagicon|NED}} World Open [[Almere]] * November 4: #30 {{flagicon|LVA}} World Open [[Riga]] * November 5: #31 {{flagicon|TUR}} World Open [[Ankara]] * November 11 & 12: #32 {{flagicon|POL}} World Open [[Warsaw]] * November 18 & 19: #33 {{flagicon|AUT}} World Open [[Vienna]] * November 25: #34 {{flagicon|EST}} World Open [[Tallinn]] * December 2 & 3: #35 {{flagicon|SVN}} World Open [[Maribor]] * December 3: #36 {{flagicon|LTU}} World Open [[Vilnius]] * December 16: #37 (final) {{flagicon|LVA}} World Open [[Riga]]
