'''Al-Kahrabaa football club''' ({{lang-ar|نادي الكهرباء الرياضي|lit=Electric Club or Electricity Club}}) is an Iraqi football club based in [[Al-Rusafa, Iraq|Rusafa District]], East Districts of the [[Tigris River]], [[Baghdad]].

