==Club logo controversy==

During some time, this club used a badge that was very similar to the one used by [[Defensor Sporting]] a club based in [[Montevideo, Uruguay|Montevideo]].<ref>"http://cafefutbol.blogspot.com/2009/09/imitacion-ilimitada-copias-en-el-otro.html"</ref>

