'''Hernán Madrid''' (born April 2, 1981) was a naturalized [[Palestinian National Authority|Palestinian]] [[association football|football]] [[Defender (association football)|defender]], who played for Wadi Al-Nes.{{Citation needed|date=July 2010}} He is currently assistant coach to [[Fernando Vergara]] in ''Deportes Iquique'', [[Chile]].
