The '''Hungary national beach handball team''' is the national team of [[Hungary]]. It is governed by the [[Hungarian Handball Federation]] and takes part in international [[beach handball]] competitions.<ref>[http://www.ihf.info/files/CompetitionData/e3d4d272-1e04-4311-94b7-cb5909d3a4be/pdf/ARG.pdf 2018 World Championship roster]</ref>

==World Championships results==
*[[2004 Beach Handball World Championships|2004]] – 6th place
*[[2006 Beach Handball World Championships|2006]] – 5th place
*[[2008 Beach Handball World Championships|2008]] – 7th place
*[[2010 Beach Handball World Championships|2010]] – 2nd place
*[[2016 Beach Handball World Championships|2016]] – 4th place
*[[2018 Men's Beach Handball World Championships|2018]] – 3rd place

